SPEED OPTIMIZATION RULE #1: Always optimize for HUMAN VISITORS! (not speed tests)
Optimize for humans!
Why Google Pagespeed, Pingdom, andÂ GTmetrixÂ scores donâ€™t matterHow to optimize for Google Pagespeed, Pingdom, andÂ GTmetrixKeep in mind that mobile is slower, making speed differences more noticeable.
SKILL:
BEGINNER â€“ can Google and follow instructions.INTERMEDIATE â€“ working as WordPress contractor.ADVANCED â€“ programmer or server-admin.
IMPACT:
