The Facebook comment is also a great option and FREE. Itâ€™s fantastic for getting tons of engagement and doesnâ€™t show all comments at once (like Disqus). It also racks up your Facebook share count number with each comment. I only donâ€™t like it because of the external loads.
Please, no Thrive Comments! If youâ€™re attracted to Disqus you might consider Commento but beware (you canâ€™t migrate there natively from WordPress, yetâ€¦you have to pass through Disqus first).
